title: 'Dragnet [Supply]: {{.DragnetID}} — Unpinned GitHub Action Reference'
id: {{.ID}}
status: experimental
description: |
  Detects GitHub Actions workflow files that reference an action using a mutable tag
  (e.g. @v3) rather than a pinned commit SHA (e.g. @sha256:...). Mutable tag references
  are vulnerable to supply chain compromise if the action author's account is taken over.
  Incident: {{.DragnetID}}
  {{.Description}}
references:
{{- range .References}}
  - {{.}}
{{- end}}
author: dragnet-bot
date: {{.Date}}
tags:
  - attack.t1195.002
  - dragnet.supply-chain
{{- range .Tags}}
  - {{.}}
{{- end}}
logsource:
  product: github
  category: github_actions_workflow
detection:
  selection:
    uses|re: '^{{range .PackageNames}}{{.}}{{end}}@v[0-9]'
  condition: selection
falsepositives:
  - Intentional use of a mutable tag in a trusted, monitored action
level: informational